      • test5

        public void test5()
        Test 5 checks 5.30pm Thursday 25 March 2004 converts to a timeline value and back again correctly. As it is in the excluded segment, we expect it to map to 9am, Friday 26 March 2004. This is prior to Daylight Saving.

      • test6

        public void test6()
        Test 6 checks that 9am on Sunday 28 March 2004 converts to the timeline value and back again correctly. Note that Saturday and Sunday are excluded from the timeline, so we expect the value to map to 9am on Monday 29 March 2004. This is during daylight saving.
